<subSubSection id="DCEBEF8CFFF0FFC3FF7AF981FD257C71" pageId="5" pageNumber="212" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="944EBC07FFF0FFC3FF7AF981FD257C71" blockId="5.[151,1074,1539,1658]" pageId="5" pageNumber="212">
REMARKS: The male of this species is recognized by a retrolateral extension on the male bulb (
<figureCitation id="0CCAA082FFF0FFC3FEA3F9A1FE527C31" box="[314,391,1571,1594]" captionStart="FIGS 11-14" captionStartId="5.[560,603,1373,1394]" captionTargetBox="[255,947,236,1301]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[151,1073,228,1315]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGS 11-14 Hersilia martensi. (11) Left male palp, ventral view. (12) TA, ventral view. (13) Ditto, prolateral view. (14) Ditto, retrolateral view. Scale line = 1.0 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/305443/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="212">Fig. 11</figureCitation>
), by a curved embolus gradually narrowing towards its sharply pointed apex (
<figureCitation id="0CCAA082FFF0FFC3FEA9F9C1FE727C51" box="[304,423,1603,1626]" captionStart="FIGS 11-14" captionStartId="5.[560,603,1373,1394]" captionTargetBox="[255,947,236,1301]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[151,1073,228,1315]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGS 11-14 Hersilia martensi. (11) Left male palp, ventral view. (12) TA, ventral view. (13) Ditto, prolateral view. (14) Ditto, retrolateral view. Scale line = 1.0 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/305443/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="212">Figs 11-14</figureCitation>
), and by the TA carrying a lightly sclerotized prolateral process and a membranous retrolateral flange (
<figureCitation id="0CCAA082FFF0FFC3FDF2F9E1FD367C71" box="[619,739,1635,1658]" captionStart="FIGS 11-14" captionStartId="5.[560,603,1373,1394]" captionTargetBox="[255,947,236,1301]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[151,1073,228,1315]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGS 11-14 Hersilia martensi. (11) Left male palp, ventral view. (12) TA, ventral view. (13) Ditto, prolateral view. (14) Ditto, retrolateral view. Scale line = 1.0 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/305443/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="212">Figs 12-14</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="DCEBEF8CFFF3FFC0FF4DFF61FE947B51" pageId="6" pageNumber="213" type="distribution">
